09:29.785 --> 09:31.615
♪ Baby, why ya leave me? ♪

09:31.621 --> 09:33.621
(PHONE RINGING)

09:33.623 --> 09:35.785
♪ And if it wasn't for the music ♪

09:35.791 --> 09:38.842
♪ I don't know what I'd do ♪

09:40.012 --> 09:41.758
